$COMMENTBLOCK$
$PROJECTNAME$ version $PROJECTVERSIONNUMBER$


	$PROJECTDESCRIPTION$


License

	see COPYING file


Compilation

	* Getting the source
		git clone git://github.com/$PROJECTREPOSITORY$/$PROJECTNAME$.git
		cd $PROJECTNAME$
		git submodule update -i

	* External libraries
		1) You can get all external libraries using a python script:
			cd 3rdParty
			python init.py
		2) Use libraries installed on your computer
			In this case, you need to edit the project-config.jam script

	* Compilation
		see INSTALL file


Tested compilers

	* Linux
		+ GCC 4.4.1 on OpenSUSE 11.2
	* MacOS
		+ GCC 4.2.1 on OSX 10.5 Leopard
	* Windows
		+ GCC-MINGW 4.3.0 on Windows XP.


